name: Buy Low Sell High
description: Buy Low Sell High is a stock market game made to be easy to learn, fast-paced, and fun. The goal is to make as much money as you can starting with just $5,000. Good luck, have fun!
minimum_requirements: OS: Windows 7/8/10 Processor: 2.0 GHz Dual core Memory: 2 GB RAM Graphics: NVIDIA GT210 or ATI HD 7730 DirectX: Version 9.0c Storage: 1 GB available space
recommended_requirements: OS: Windows 7/8/10 Processor: Intel Core i5 Memory: 4 GB RAM Graphics: NVIDIA GT 440 or better, ATI 7950 or better DirectX: Version 11 Storage: 1 GB available space
